### Template Access Control

#### [MODIFY] [templates.js](file:///e:/project/Intern-logbook/server/routes/templates.js)
- Add `verifyToken` middleware to the GET `/` route
- When listing templates, also fetch user's `allowedTemplates` from Firestore
- Add `allowed` boolean field to each template in response
- Add a new route `GET /api/templates/check-access/:filename` that verifies the current user has access to a specific template

